One way to do this is to use an invisible graphic as a clickable element that covers the chart area. That is, add the following 'graphic' option to your chart
```
var chart_width = 1000
var chart_height = 200

function(params) {
  console.log('CLICK')
}

{graphic: {
  type: 'rect',
  shape: {
    x: 0,
    y: 0,
    height: chart_height,
    width: chart_width
  },
  onclick: onClick,
  invisible: true,
  z: 100
}}
```

